; BiomechIQ install config.
; The SDK-53 + VisionCamera v4 stack has a couple of benign peer-range
; mismatches (e.g. victory-native vs the SDK-pinned Skia pre-release), so
; installs use legacy peer resolution. Keeps `npm install` / `npm ci` green
; locally and in CI without per-command flags.
legacy-peer-deps=true
